📌 What is Amazon Aurora?
            Amazon Aurora is AWS's own cloud-native relational database engine   
            — fully compatible with MySQL and PostgreSQL but built from scratch by AWS to be faster, 
            more reliable, and more scalable than standard RDS MySQL/PostgreSQL.

📊 Aurora Architecture — How it's Different:
            Standard RDS MySQL:
            ┌─────────────────────────────────┐
            │  EC2-like Instance              │
            │  ┌───────────┐  ┌────────────┐  │
            │  │  MySQL    │  │  EBS       │  │
            │  │  Engine   │  │  Storage   │  │
            │  └───────────┘  └────────────┘  │
            │  (Compute + Storage TOGETHER)   │
            │  Single AZ by default           │
            └─────────────────────────────────┘
            
            Amazon Aurora:
            ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
            │  Aurora Instance (Compute)                       │
            │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
            │  │  Aurora Engine (MySQL/PostgreSQL compat) │   │
            │  └──────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
            │                    │                             │
            │  ┌─────────────────▼──────────────────────────┐ │
            │  │       Aurora Distributed Storage           │ │
            │  │  6 copies across 3 Availability Zones      │ │
            │  │  AZ-1: Copy 1 ✅  Copy 2 ✅               │ │
            │  │  AZ-2: Copy 3 ✅  Copy 4 ✅               │ │
            │  │  AZ-3: Copy 5 ✅  Copy 6 ✅               │ │
            │  └────────────────────────────────────────────┘ │
            │  (Compute + Storage SEPARATED — highly durable)  │
            └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
Feature	            RDS MySQL	            Amazon Aurora
Performance	            Baseline	            5x faster ✅
Storage	            Up to 64TB	            Up to 128TB ✅
Storage Auto-scale	Manual	            Automatic ✅
Copies	            2 (Multi-AZ)	6 across 3 AZs ✅
