Failover Time	60-120 seconds	< 30 seconds ✅
Self-healing	❌ No	            ✅ Yes
Serverless	            ❌ No	            ✅ Yes
Global Database	❌ No	            ✅ Yes
Free Tier	            ✅ Yes	            ❌ No
Cost	            Lower 💰	            Higher 💸
Local Development	✅ Yes	            ❌ No
Beginner Friendly	✅ Yes	            ❌ Complex
Best For	            Learning / Small apps	Enterprise / High traffic
